entries.title: Global ransomware campaign has US and European officials on alert
entries.description: A new global ransomware campaign has hit at least 3,800 victims, including hundreds in the US, according to crowdsourced data reviewed by CNN, prompting warnings from European and US cybersecurity officials.

entries.title: Al Hilal shock Flamengo with 3-2 win in Club World Cup semifinal
entries.description: Saudi Arabia's Al Hilal stunned South American champions Flamengo to reach the Club World Cup final with a 3-2 victory on Tuesday thanks to two penalties from Salem Al Dawsari and a close-range strike from Luciano Vietto.
